  <entry>
    <title>Html基础</title>
    <url>/2022/05/03/Html%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="HTML"><a href="#HTML" class="headerlink" title="HTML"></a>HTML</h3><p>简单的html页面架构</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="keyword">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>一个完整的页面主要包括：html，head，body</p>
<p>其中<html>标签是整个页面的框架，内包含<head>和</head><body>标签</body></html></p>
<p>head：定义文档的头部，是头部元素的容器</p>
<p>body：定义文档的主体，包含文档的所有内容</p>
<p>此外还可以在HTML第一行，html标签前加入 <!DOCTYPE html> 告诉浏览器这是一个HTML5页面</p>
<h1 id="标签"><a href="#标签" class="headerlink" title="标签"></a>标签</h1><p>HTML文档由HTML元素定义，HTML元素即<strong>标签</strong>。</p>
<p>大多数为<strong>双标签</strong>（拥有<strong>起始标签(opening tag)<strong>和</strong>闭合标签(closing tag)<strong>），</strong>单标签</strong>在起始标签中闭合。</p>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span> 这是一个段落 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span> 这是一个段落 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>大多数的标签可以进行<strong>嵌套</strong>。</p>
<h1 id="属性"><a href="#属性" class="headerlink" title="属性"></a>属性</h1><p>HTML元素可以在标签中设置属性，<strong>属性</strong>一般描述于<strong>开始标签</strong>。</p>
<p>属性总以 <strong>键值对</strong> 的形式出现。</p>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span> = <span class="string">&quot;https://www.baidu.com&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 百度 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>href属性指明链接的地址。</p>
<h1 id="常用标签"><a href="#常用标签" class="headerlink" title="常用标签"></a>常用标签</h1><h2 id="注释"><a href="#注释" class="headerlink" title="注释"></a>注释</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 这是一个注释 --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="html标题"><a href="#html标题" class="headerlink" title="html标题"></a>html标题</h2><p>标题(Heading)通过**&lt;h1&gt;-&lt;h6&gt;**进行定义。</p>
<p>&lt;h1&gt;定义最大的标题，&lt;h6&gt;定义最小的标题。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span> 这是标题1 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span> 这是标题2 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>（html标题标签仅用于标题，不要为了改变字体样式而去使用，搜索引擎的爬虫会根据标题给你的网页生成索引结构，文档的结构非常重要）</p>
<h2 id="水平线"><a href="#水平线" class="headerlink" title="水平线"></a>水平线</h2><p>**<hr>**标签在html页面中创建水平线（horizontal）。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span> 段落1 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span> 段落2 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span> 段落3 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="段落"><a href="#段落" class="headerlink" title="段落"></a>段落</h2><p>标签创建一个段落(paragraph)。


<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span> 段落1 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



</p><h2 id="换行符"><a href="#换行符" class="headerlink" title="换行符"></a>换行符</h2><p>**&lt;br&gt;**标签用于换行符（break row）。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span> 这是一个<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span>段落 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="文本格式化"><a href="#文本格式化" class="headerlink" title="文本格式化"></a>文本格式化</h2><p>标签<strong>&lt;b&gt;(bold)和&lt;i&gt;(italic)<strong>分别表示</strong>加粗</strong>和<strong>斜体</strong>。</p>
<p>通常使用**&lt;strong&gt;代替&lt;b&gt;<strong>，</strong>&lt;em&gt;代替&lt;i&gt;**。</p>
<p>strong和em表示渲染的文本是<strong>重要</strong>的。</p>
<p>常用文本格式化标签如下：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>标签</th>
<th>描述</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>&lt;b&gt;</td>
<td>定义粗体文字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;big&gt;</td>
<td>插入大号字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;em&gt;</td>
<td>定义着重文字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;i&gt;</td>
<td>定义斜体字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;small&gt;</td>
<td>定义小号字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;strong&gt;</td>
<td>定义加重语气</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;sub&gt;</td>
<td>定义下标字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;sup&gt;</td>
<td>定义上标字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;ins&gt;</td>
<td>定义插入字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;del&gt;</td>
<td>定义删除字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;s&gt;</td>
<td>不建议使用，&lt;del&gt;代替</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;strike&gt;</td>
<td>不建议使用，&lt;del&gt;代替</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;u&gt;</td>
<td>不建议使用，使用style代替</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>计算机输出标签：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>标签</th>
<th>描述</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>&lt;code&gt;</td>
<td>定义计算机代码</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;kbd&gt;</td>
<td>定义键盘码</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;samp&gt;</td>
<td>定义计算机代码样本</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;tt&gt;</td>
<td>定义打字机代码</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;var&gt;</td>
<td>定义变量</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;pre&gt;</td>
<td>定义预格式文本</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;listing&gt;</td>
<td>不建议，使用&lt;pre&gt;代替</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;plaintext&gt;</td>
<td>不建议，使用&lt;pre&gt;代替</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;xmp&gt;</td>
<td>不建议，使用&lt;pre&gt;代替</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>引用、引用和术语定义：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>标签</th>
<th>描述</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>&lt;abbr&gt;</td>
<td>定义缩写</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;acronym&gt;</td>
<td>定义首字母缩写</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;address&gt;</td>
<td>定义地址</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;bdo&gt;</td>
<td>定义文字方向</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;blockquote&gt;</td>
<td>定义长引用</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;q&gt;</td>
<td>定义短引用</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;cite&gt;</td>
<td>定义引用、引证</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;dfn&gt;</td>
<td>定义一个定义项目</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h2><p>**&lt;q&gt;**元素包围短引用。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">q</span>&gt;</span> 这是一个引用 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">q</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>**&lt;blockquote&gt;**元素包围长引用。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span> 这是一个长引用 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>&lt;abbr&gt;定义缩写或首字母缩略语。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">abbr</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">&quot;World Health Organization&quot;</span>&gt;</span>WHO<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">abbr</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="定义"><a href="#定义" class="headerlink" title="定义"></a>定义</h2><p>**&lt;dfn&gt;**用于定义。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dfn</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">&quot;World Health Organization&quot;</span>&gt;</span>WHO<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dfn</span>&gt;</span> 成立于 1948 年。<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="著作的标题"><a href="#著作的标题" class="headerlink" title="著作的标题"></a>著作的标题</h2><p><strong>&lt;cite&gt;<strong>用于著作的标题。通常是</strong>斜体</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">cite</span>&gt;</span>The Scream<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">cite</span>&gt;</span> by Edward Munch. Painted in 1893.<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="双向重写"><a href="#双向重写" class="headerlink" title="双向重写"></a>双向重写</h2><p>**&lt;bdo&gt;**用于文本的双向重写：</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">bdo</span> <span class="attr">dir</span>=<span class="string">&quot;rtl&quot;</span>&gt;</span>This text will be written from right to left<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">bdo</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>前端</tag>
      </tags>
